About Event

​We're hosting a celebration of pixel art and its cultural impact, tracing the inspiration from CryptoPunks that sparked an exciting digital art movement across Asia, particularly in Japan. This meetup brings together the vibrant art community—artists, collectors, and enthusiasts alike—to connect and share their passion for pixel art culture.

​Title

​Onchain Harmony: Punks & Pixels A Celebration of Digital Art Culture

​Event Description

​Join us for an intimate celebration of pi
